by-name-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   成功，返回关联数组， 如果信息未找到则返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.geoip-region-by-name-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><div class="example" id="example-3661">    <p><strong>示例 #1  <span class="function"><strong>geoip_region_by_name()</strong></span> 例子：</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><p>     以下示例将会打印对应 example.com 主机的包含国家和地区代码的关联数组。    </p></div>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;white-space:pre-wrap"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br>$region </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">geoip_region_by_name</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'www.example.com'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>if (</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$region</span><span style="color: #007700">) {<br>    </span><span style="color: #9876AA">print_r</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$region</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br>}<br></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>    <div class="example-contents"><p>以上示例会输出：</p></div>    <div class="example-contents screen" style="border-color:gray;background:#1E1F22;"><div class="examplescode"><blockquote style="border:1px gray solid;">Array<br>(<br>    [country_code] =&gt; US<br>    [region] =&gt; CA<br>)</blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>   </div></div>
